{"tid":1938403,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"意大利「專家」：武漢肺炎來自意大利","createTime":"2020-03-22T13:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T02:23:50.000Z","uid":122940,"like":14,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f57cbe5094edf4f7d462c8f04f9f4cad5873acd7","tid":1938403,"uid":122940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:42:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/451010/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%89%8D-%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%88%96%E5%B7%B2%E6%96%BC%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F451010%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%2589%258D-%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%2592%25AD&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=b7e1e6ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/451010/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%89%8D-%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%88%96%E5%B7%B2%E6%96%BC%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD</a><br />\n<br />\n美國全國公共廣播電台（NPR）引述意大利醫生雷穆西（Giuseppe Remuzzi）表示，目前意大利的醫療系統人手不足，其他科目的醫生亦要加入，如學習操作呼吸機救治新冠肺炎患者。<br />\n<br />\n雷穆西指出，他從其他全科醫生中聽說，在2019年11月或12時當地曾出現奇怪的肺炎，在老齡人身上發病十分嚴重。他指出這可能表示早在意大利意識病毒在中國爆發時，病毒已在倫巴第地區出現，使當地在2月急速爆發時令人措手不及。<br />\n<br />\n報道指中國的肺炎病例同樣早在2019年11月期間出現，目前未知雷穆西所指的個案是否與病毒有關，亦未知是否與中國爆發的疫情有關連。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好好笑﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變「意大利肺炎」。意佬為奶共而要賣國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1397ab3014c29ad45cbbefca9eeaae5279606cb7","tid":1938403,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />意大利"},{"pid":"8596a709211f838588f130baea8286b1fd440303","tid":1938403,"uid":1049,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"美國唔食死貓就求其搵第二度接手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁癡線都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b14a533694e3055895421605d5f612855947ff3","tid":1938403,"uid":54824,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"係溫州人帶病毒入意大利！"},{"pid":"c53bd7b87d548f9c0ad4bee318eeda90d55a8e29","tid":1938403,"uid":122940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8596a709211f838588f130baea8286b1fd440303","tid":1938403,"uid":1049,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"美國唔食死貓就求其搵第二度接手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁癡線都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:51:53.000Z","msg":"意佬為一帶一路肯認晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651126e18acbdb01762a8b57029fb60848912b4c","tid":1938403,"uid":298012,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q47jxFy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi